[4.67, "o", "\r\n"]
[4.76, "o", "OFFLINE: off-machine network egress is hard-blocked (loopback / local Ollama allowed).\r\n"]
[4.85, "o", "\r\n"]
[4.94, "o", "NOTE: heuristic backend is an OFFLINE STUB with near-zero recall. Use it to test the\r\n"]
[5.03, "o", "plumbing only; choose --backend local or cloud for a real audit.\r\n"]
[5.12, "o", "\r\n"]
[5.67, "o", "  analyzing 10/15 ...\r\n"]
[6.22, "o", "  analyzing 15/15 ...\r\n"]
[6.31, "o", "============================================================================\r\n"]
[6.4, "o", " exposurecheck  --  re-identification risk (no-dossier)\r\n"]
[6.49, "o", "============================================================================\r\n"]
[6.58, "o", " backend     : heuristic\r\n"]
[6.67, "o", " platforms   : reddit, twitter\r\n"]
[6.76, "o", " posts       : 15 parsed | 15 analyzed | 0 empty skipped\r\n"]
[6.85, "o", " scope       : public posts + profile + media metadata. NOT analyzed: likes, DMs, image content.\r\n"]
[6.94, "o", "\r\n"]
[7.24, "o", " !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\r\n"]
[7.33, "o", " INCOMPLETE - heuristic backend (offline stub, near-zero recall).\r\n"]
[7.42, "o", " This is NOT a real audit and NOT an all-clear: it flags only obvious\r\n"]
[7.51, "o", " patterns and misses most AI re-identification signal. Whether or not\r\n"]
[7.6, "o", " cards appear below, re-run with  --backend local  (offline, private)\r\n"]
[7.69, "o", " or  --backend cloud  for a real assessment.\r\n"]
[7.99, "o", " !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\r\n"]
[8.08, "o", "\r\n"]
[8.17, "o", " Handling: even masked, this report can identify you in combination\r\n"]
[8.26, "o", " (subreddit + date + category). Keep it local - don't paste it, screenshot\r\n"]
[8.35, "o", " it, or store it in a cloud-synced folder.\r\n"]
[8.44, "o", "\r\n"]
[8.74, "o", " [HIGH] LOCATION  (score 100.0)\r\n"]
[8.83, "o", "        8 signals - 7 posts - sources: exif, metadata, text\r\n"]
[8.92, "o", "        Why: Repeated place, commute and neighbourhood clues across many\r\n"]
[9.01, "o", "        posts can narrow your home area far more than any single post\r\n"]
[9.1, "o", "        suggests.\r\n"]
[9.19, "o", "        Examples (masked):\r\n"]
[9.28, "o", "          - [self-set location field] | @sampleuser\r\n"]
[9.37, "o", "          - [image GPS in EXIF] | 1500000000000000005-AbCd1234.jpg\r\n"]
[9.46, "o", "          - [location clue] | r/SampleCity | 2023-04-02\r\n"]
[9.55, "o", "        To review: 6 of your own posts (reveal in-session)\r\n"]
[9.64, "o", "        Reduce:\r\n"]
[9.73, "o", "          - Generalise specifics - region not neighbourhood, 'a coastal\r\n"]
[9.82, "o", "            city' not the exact route.\r\n"]
[9.91, "o", "          - Strip image EXIF/GPS before posting; re-check older media.\r\n"]
[10.0, "o", "\r\n"]
[10.3, "o", " [HIGH] ACCOUNT LINKAGE  (score 70.6)\r\n"]
[10.39, "o", "        2 signals - 1 post - sources: exif, metadata\r\n"]
[10.48, "o", "        Why: Outbound links, reused handles and device fingerprints stitch\r\n"]
[10.57, "o", "        this pseudonymous account to your other identities.\r\n"]
[10.66, "o", "        Examples (masked):\r\n"]
[10.75, "o", "          - [outbound website link] | @sampleuser\r\n"]
[10.84, "o", "          - [camera make/model in EXIF] | 1500000000000000005-AbCd1234.jpg\r\n"]
[10.93, "o", "        Reduce:\r\n"]
[11.02, "o", "          - Remove outbound links to personal sites; don't reuse this handle.\r\n"]
[11.11, "o", "          - Strip device make/model from image EXIF.\r\n"]
[11.2, "o", "\r\n"]
[12.2, "o", "cora:~$ "]
